For a customer, we managed to fix the database inconsistency by running this query : 
{noformat}
select * from workflowschemeentity where workflow not in (select workflowname from jiraworkflows);{noformat}

This basically lists all workflow that exist in a scheme but are not present in  workflow table.

This should have been caught by the integrity checker.

